### Pre-Completion Grep Check

Run this before marking any component or page task as done:

```bash
# Find any remaining border-subtle in divider/separator contexts
grep -rn "border-subtle" client/pages/ client/components/ --include="*.css" --include="*.tsx"
```

Flag any result where the element is a **section divider, table row, or preview card border** — those must use `separator`.
